platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 美しい世界で解く新感覚のパズル

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Explore a gorgeous island packed with intricately interwoven puzzles. There’s a subtle logic to the world design that connects structures, land configurations, and puzzle grids. For persistent adventurers, The Witness is an unforgettable experience.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: 作り込まれたパズルを解き進め、島に隠された謎を見つけ出そう。
Beautiful, challenging, and always inventive - these brilliant puzzles will really test you.
Ils sont magnifiques, mais ils vous donneront du fil à retordre.
